To upgrade OLAS from version 1.1 to version 1.2:

- The directory 20121211113000 should be placed under the existing
  releases directory

- Verify that the symbolic link for log/ resolves to the shared/log/ directory

- Verify that the file config/databases.yml resolves to the existing version
  in the shared/config/ directory

- Apply the update_1.2.sql script using mysql

    mysql -u USERNAME -p -h HOSTNAME DATABASE_NAME < scripts/update_1.2.sql

- Change the symbolic link "current" to point to releases/20121211113000
